new post: just copy paste

categories can be a word, or a list of words, e.g.

categories: Sass

or

categories: [CSS3, Sass, Media Queries]

or

categories:
- CSS3
- Sass
- Media Queries

to read locally:

bundle exec jekyll serve # port 4000

to publish:

bundle exec jekyll build # not necessary if you've been using `serve`
./rsync.sh
